{"tid":2241693,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［有圖］懲教所最黑暗既一面，好多手足係入面比黑懲欺壓","createTime":"2020-10-13T13:14:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-13T13:21:50.000Z","uid":188515,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b16ba1060833a93dbd4d5a0a6d137f62a54f0154","tid":2241693,"uid":188515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T13:14:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qLQnqJt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqLQnqJt.jpg&h=dab89db3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mrr57WP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMrr57WP.jpg&h=212344b0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uvviJvb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuvviJvb.jpg&h=5962ccf0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1gm9Qac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1gm9Qac.jpg&h=b6970aaa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LEvKD3z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLEvKD3z.jpg&h=1d339c96&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A4gRi3A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA4gRi3A.jpg&h=eda9d55a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dT9Lovh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdT9Lovh.jpg&h=fc75301c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zS9SNWY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzS9SNWY.jpg&h=6d53c248&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rL1t5JF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrL1t5JF.jpg&h=926bbbf5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇到呢到<br />\n其實都係想大家能夠關注入面既手足<br />\n唔好當佢地係condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n得閒既就寫下信安慰下佢地<br />\n多啲探下佢地<br />\n比錢出嚟等還押既手足食好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />